{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script aims to reproduce the folder separation in a way Logic X does it.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Draw separator on folder track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script aimes to provide a mechanism similar to the one in LogicProX to separate folders in the Arrange View.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Options\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 TRACK_HEIGHT\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 this MUST be AT LEAST 2 pixels higher than the size defined in Preferences > Apparence > Media > "Hide labels for items when item take lane height is less than". You also have to uncheck "draw labels above items, rather than within items" Default value is 28 but I got better result with 20pixels. Default 6 and dafault 5 theme TRACK_HEIGHT=25. Also work with Jane, Funktion, Other tested themes and values : iLogic V2 = 28 iLogic V3 = 24 Flat Madness and CubeXD= 22\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 TRACK_COLOR_SINGLE\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 do you want all the item folder to get the same color ? Otherwise, default folder track color will be used. Default is 0\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ##TRACK_COLOR use RGB color code. Default is \{111,121,131\}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 TRACK_COLOR_DARKER_STEP\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 this is the amount of darkness yo uwant to apply to default track color. 0 means NO darkness. Default is 25\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 User profile https://forum.cockos.com/member.php?u=153781\par}
}

